/*
 * This file is a part of the SchemaSpy project (http://schemaspy.sourceforge.net).
 * Copyright (C) 2004, 2005, 2006, 2007, 2008, 2009, 2010, 2011 John Currier
 *
 * SchemaSpy is free software; you can redistribute it and/or
